really familiar to you.

00:01:00.650 --> 00:01:02.060 align:middle line:84%
It's the same
state of relaxation

00:01:02.060 --> 00:01:04.860 align:middle line:90%
you go into as you fall asleep.

00:01:04.860 --> 00:01:06.980 align:middle line:84%
So it's a really natural
state to be into,

00:01:06.980 --> 00:01:09.380 align:middle line:90%
and it's really safe as well.

00:01:09.380 --> 00:01:11.720 align:middle line:84%
When you're in that
lovely relaxed state,

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:14.930 align:middle line:84%
