means that any messaging will

00:01:17.510 --> 00:01:20.120 align:middle line:84%
bypass your conscious
mind and instead

00:01:20.120 --> 00:01:22.580 align:middle line:90%
go into your subconscious mind.

00:01:22.580 --> 00:01:25.400 align:middle line:10%
The reason we want to access
your subconscious mind

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:28.400 align:middle line:10%
is because that's where your
permanent thoughts, beliefs,

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:30.320 align:middle line:10%
habits, and memories live.

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:32.840 align:middle line:10%
So by talking directly to
your subconscious mind,

00:01:32.840 --> 00:01:34.910 align:middle line:10%
we're able to make real changes.

00:01:34.910 --> 00:01:38.090 align:middle line:84%
We can reframe, rewire,
and retrain your mind

00:01:38.090 --> 00:01:41.150 align:middle line:84%
to eliminate any of those
negative thinking patterns

00:01:41.150 --> 00:01:44.090 align:middle line:84%
and instead replace with
empowering positive changes

00:01:44.090 --> 00:01:47.660 align:middle line:90%
once and for all.

00:01:47.660 --> 00:01:52.460 align:middle line:84%
We recommend that you listen to
our audios at least four times.

00:01:52.460 --> 00:01:54.290 align:middle line:84%
In that way, you're
able to override

00:01:54.290 --> 00:01:55.970 align:middle line:84%
any of those negative
thinking patterns

00:01:55.970 --> 00:01:59.300 align:middle line:84%
and really compound the
positivity again and again

00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:01.190 align:middle line:90%
and really make those changes.

00:02:01.190 --> 00:02:03.290 align:middle line:10%
And you'll be creating
new positive neural

00:02:03.290 --> 00:02:06.510 align:middle line:10%
pathways within your mind
each time you do that.

00:02:06.510 --> 00:02:09.360 align:middle line:90%
So it's really important.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:12.117 align:middle line:84%
You can listen to our audios
at any time of day or night.

00:02:12.117 --> 00:02:13.700 align:middle line:84%
But we suggest that
you listen to them

00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:15.320 align:middle line:90%
when you're not too tired.

00:02:15.320 --> 00:02:18.140 align:middle line:84%
