deep, deep state of sleep,

00:02:18.140 --> 00:02:22.790 align:middle line:84%
then your subconscious mind
just won't be listening.

00:02:22.790 --> 00:02:25.240 align:middle line:84%
So do make sure that you're
listening to our audios

00:02:25.240 --> 00:02:26.980 align:middle line:84%
when you're free from
any distractions.

00:02:26.980 --> 00:02:30.910 align:middle line:84%
Please don't listen to them when
you're actively doing anything

00:02:30.910 --> 00:02:34.110 align:middle line:84%
like driving or
operating machinery.

00:02:34.110 --> 00:02:35.790 align:middle line:84%
If there's an
emergency and you need

00:02:35.790 --> 00:02:38.100 align:middle line:84%
to come out of hypnosis
before we awaken you,

00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.810 align:middle line:90%
that's absolutely fine.

00:02:39.810 --> 00:02:41.545 align:middle line:84%
Your subconscious
mind will allow you

00:02:41.545 --> 00:02:43.170 align:middle line:84%
and you'll easily
come out of hypnosis.

00:02:43.170 --> 00:02:46.650 align:middle line:84%
So it will be just like waking
up from a nap or from a sleep.

